snippet.title: Atari 50: The Anniversary Celebration Trailer
snippet.description:
The history of Atari told through never-before-seen content, candid interviews, and more than 90 games, including six new titles inspired by the classics. 

Developed by the team at Digital Eclipse. Coming in November 2022.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1919470/Atari_50_The_Anniversary_Celebration/

Join us in our official Discord server: https://discord.gg/atariclub
